## Local development environment variables
## Copy to `.env.local` (DO NOT commit `.env.local`) and fill with real values.
#
## JWT
JWT_SECRET=change_me_to_a_long_random_string
#
## AI provider (Groq/OpenAI-compatible)
AI_API_KEY=change_me
#
## Database
## Recommended: provide a full JDBC URL via DATABASE_URL as required by `application.yml`.
## Example:
## DATABASE_URL=jdbc:postgresql://localhost:5432/finance_coach_db?user=postgres&password=postgres
DATABASE_URL=jdbc:postgresql://localhost:5432/finance_coach_db?user=postgres&password=postgres
#
## Server
PORT=8080
